Content.Text:
<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Oh, it's you. Your face is sorta hard
to remember. It's like... insignificant.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Oh, 'morning. It's hard to get started
early in the morning, y'know?
<PAGE>
Hey, why don't you give me a present
to perk me up? You don't have any?
You don't know the ropes yet, do you?

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
I'm surprised that you came to this
town, <MYNAME>. There's nothing here.
<PAGE>
I'm sticking around 'cuz you said you're
gonna improve the town, but who knows
what the Goddess sees in this place.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Oh, it's you. My little brother is
pretty dense. It's irritating.
<PAGE>
<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>I'm embarrassed to be his sister... But
well, he's a good person.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
What, <MYNAME> What do you want? If it's
nothing important, I'll get mad.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
What is it? Don't just stand there. If
you have something to say, say it.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
If you wander around at this hour,
you'll trip or something. Hurry up and
go home.
<PAGE>
<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>Stupid! I'm not worried. It's just a
warning. A simple warning!

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Perfect timing, <MYNAME>. I'm tired from
serving the Harvest Goddess all day.
Massage my shoulders, will you?
<PAGE>
<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>Hurry it up. Ah, that feels great. All
the fatigue is being massaged away.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Oh, good evening. How is the town 
building coming along?
<PAGE>
Do your best. I'm rooting for you.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Oh, it's you. It's gotten warmer in our
forest and lots of buds are sprouting.
<PAGE>
You live here, so you're welcome to
take some home. Just don't take too
many.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
It's hot outside. How come you look so
cool? Aren't you hot?
<PAGE>
<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>I may be a Harvest Sprite, but when it's
hot, it's hot! Any complaints?

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
I don't like autumn...because the
Harvest Goddess has a huge appetite.
<PAGE>
And harvesting enough food for her to
eat is a huge challenge.
<PAGE>
<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>*sigh* I have to keep going back and
forth between the spring and forest
and it's never enough.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
It's so hard to walk because of the
snow. We're short in height and get
buried in no time at all.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
I'll have to work hard again today to
protect the land. Managing the land is
hard work, you know.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
My hobby? Why do you want to know 
something like that? Well, whatever.
<PAGE>
<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>My hobby is to instruct my kid brother!
He's such a klutz, he irritates me, so
I supervise him. It's fun.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Do you make offerings to the Harvest
Goddess? I've noticed an increase in
things that look like rubbish...
<PAGE>
If you're throwing out things that look
like rubbish, don't. It's a lot of work
to clean them up.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Don't tell me you think I don't look
after my kid brother? If you do, you are
wrong.
<PAGE>
<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>I'm teaching my brother to become a fine
Harvest Sprite! Oh, what a wonderful
sister I am...

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
What do you think of the Harvest Sprite
clothing? I think it's cute.
<PAGE>
But I'd like to wear different kinds
of clothes like humans do. I envy you.
<PAGE>
<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>Don't they have clothes shops for
Harvest Sprites too? If they did, I'd
go every day.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
It's exhausting to serve the Harvest
Goddess. For ages now, it's do this
or do that.
<PAGE>
<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>Although I push it all onto my kid
brother. Brothers respect their big
sisters. Hohohohoho.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
For a human, you've got willpower. I'll
admit that much. Just a little, though.
<PAGE>
Don't get me wrong now. Don't start
slacking off.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
You have something nice there. Yes, the
royal jelly! Hand it over!
<PAGE>
Mmmhmm, I love children who listen. I'm
going to enjoy eating it. Ohohoho!

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Oh, you have something nice there. It's
a present for me? How thoughtful.
<PAGE>
Mmmhmm, you know the routine. Keeping
on my good side is very smart.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
A present for me? You're good at 
buttering me up. Fine, I'll take it.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
A present? Hmm, for me? Okay, I'll
accept it.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
Are you trying to start an argument?
How can you give this for a present?
I'll give it to my little brother.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
I'm beyond getting angry. Listen, why
would I be happy to receive a present
like this?
<PAGE>
<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>Think it over carefully. I expect you to
do better next time.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
What is that in your hand?! What are
you going to do about the filth in the
shed?! A present for me?!
<PAGE>
Are you crazy?! I don't want something
like this. I'll make my brother take it!

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
Why would you take something I hate
and make it so much bigger? What
were you thinking?!
<PAGE>
I don't want like this! I'll make my
brother take it!

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
I'm in shock. What would compel you
to take something I hate so much,
and make it so big?
<PAGE>
<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>Kudos for your effort, but if I hate
something, I hate it! No matter the
size! Cripes, what am I to do?

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
I don't feel like presents today. Can
you try another time?

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
A present? I'm good for today. Go
and give it to my little brother.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Oh, a birthday present for me? Why, it's
royal jelly! Your taste is impeccable!
<PAGE>
I'm impressed, <MYNAME>! I'm
going to enjoy eating it.
Thank you!

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
My birthday present? Hmm, you know what
I like. My compliments to you.
<PAGE>
You may be a human, but you have
potential. Ohohohoho.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Oh, how thoughtful. It's unusual for a
human to give a Harvest Sprite a
birthday present.
<PAGE>
Hmm, and you presented it in an okay 
manner. This, I'll accept.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
A birthday present? How did you know it
was my birthday? Never mind. I'll
accept it.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
You call this a birthday present? What
were you thinking?! Why would you give
me something I don't like?
<PAGE>
Humans do such unbelievable things.
Grrr, humans.... Repent!

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
You have no taste in birthday
presents... I almost feel sorry for you.
<PAGE>
<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>All right, I understand. Just leave it
there. I'll give it to my little
brother.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
A birthday is special. It's the same for
humans and Harvest Sprites.
<PAGE>
And to present filth from the shed is
worse than a prank! I want nothing to
do with you!

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
Just because it's big doesn't mean it's
a good birthday present!
<PAGE>
Why would you take something I hate
and make it so much bigger? Are you
crazy? I'll make my brother take it.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
Cripes! This is my birthday present?!
What would I do with something so big?!
<PAGE>
It's not only big, it's something I
hate! You'd better think this over. Oh,
it's so irritating!

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
W-What is this? A present for Flower
Day?
<PAGE>
Hmm, what a nice day for humans. I don't
mind accepting it.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
Huh? I'm not a kid... Why give me a
Pumpkin Festival present?
<PAGE>
<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>O-Okay, I get it. Don't look so sad.
I'll accept it.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
This is a Blue Feather. Human
weddings take so much preparation.
All the emphasis is on form.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Hmm, a ring, eh? That's supposed to be
precious? Humans are strange.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Oh, my helpers. Those kids always help
me with my work.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Oh, my helpers. Those kids help me
gather foodstuffs for the Harvest
Goddess.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Oh, I'll give you something nice today.
Here you go.
<PAGE>
I heard it was your birthday, so I got
you a present. Be appreciative.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
It's your birthday today? Hmm...well,
happy birthday.
<PAGE>
<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>What's with the long face? I didn't get
you a present. Ask someone else.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
I haven't seen you lately. I was worried
that something happened. Well, as long
as you're okay.

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
What? Since you're holding that...I
guess you want grown-up candy?

<FACE_KORO2><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Okay. Then hand over that royal jelly.
